author: jacopoc
msg: Applied fix from trunk for revision: 1337789

Improved implementation of concurrent access to the cache of parsed Groovy scripts to avoid the risk of a NPE in the unlucky event that, between the execution of the cache.putIfAbsent and cache.get methods, the cache entry was removed (e.g. cache cleared/expired).

author: gstein
msg: For responses with XML bodies, trap 404 responses and handle them
(expat_response_handler): rename param to SCRATCH_POOL. look for a
404 response and pass responsibility to a handler that can figure
out what to do with that response.
